{"id":50901,"title":"Parathyroid carcinoma.","abstract":"Parathyroid carcinoma is a rare form of endocrine malignancy accounting for only a small minority of cancer cases. Due to the rarity of this cancer, there are no generalized guidelines for its management; however, surgery remains to be the mainstay therapy. The purpose of this article is to review and summarize the available literature on parathyroid carcinoma, while discussing proposed staging systems and the role of available adjuvant therapies. ","date":"2014-05-30","categories":"Endocrine System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24742584","annotations":[{"name":"Cancer staging","weight":0.72023,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cancer_staging"},{"name":"Cancer","weight":0.708098,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cancer"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.703484,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Malignancy","weight":0.689375,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malignancy"},{"name":"Carcinoma","weight":0.687788,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carcinoma"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.677347,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Parathyroid gland","weight":0.3941,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parathyroid_gland"},{"name":"Endocrine system","weight":0.386533,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Endocrine_system"},{"name":"Adjuvant","weight":0.278771,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adjuvant"},{"name":"Literature","weight":0.142977,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Literature"},{"name":"Management","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management"},{"name":"Parathyroid carcinoma","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parathyroid_carcinoma"},{"name":"Minority group","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wik